Sentencas: Anode-supported solid oxide fuel cells have been produced by water base sequential tape casting and cosintering.
Titulo: Sintering and Deformation of Solid Oxide Fuel Cells Produced by Sequential Tape Casting

Sentencas: The curvature developed upon cosintering was monitored in situ.
Titulo: Sintering and Deformation of Solid Oxide Fuel Cells Produced by Sequential Tape Casting

Sentencas: By tailoring the green microstructure, it was possible to reduce the curvature rate and to produce flat cells avoiding the need for a creep-flattening treatment.
Titulo: Sintering and Deformation of Solid Oxide Fuel Cells Produced by Sequential Tape Casting

Sentencas: The power density at 800 degrees C and 0.7V was 751.7 mW/cm(2).
Titulo: Sintering and Deformation of Solid Oxide Fuel Cells Produced by Sequential Tape Casting
